extends layout

block content

  p Welcome to <em>LocalLibrary</em>, a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li <strong> Books: </strong> !{data.book_count}
      li <strong> Copies:</strong> !{data.book_instance_count}
      li <strong> Copies available:</strong> !{data.book_instance_available_count}
      li <strong> Authors:</strong> !{data.author_count}
      li <strong> Genres:</strong> !{data.genre_count}